 {"type":"message","id":"a8410114","parentId":"ecc4b1f8","timestamp":"2026-03-29T22:52:58.517Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All checks pass. Here's a summary of everything done:\n\n## Summary\n\n### `SemanticQueryService.java` changes\n\n**New imports & fields:**\n- `ExperimentService`, `HydeService`, `SqlQueryRouter` added as injected dependencies (constructor grows from 10 to 13 params)\n\n**Three new pipeline steps in `query()`:**\n\n**(A) SQL routing check** — inserted after intent classification, before filter/namespace/embedding:\n- If `sqlQueryRouter.canHandle(intent, keywords)` → calls `sqlQueryRouter.query(...)` \n- If result is available → returns `RagQueryResult` with `ConfidenceTier.HIGH` immediately (no vector search)\n- If SQL query fails → logs and falls through to vector search\n\n**(B) HyDE experiment check** — inserted after namespace resolution, before embedding:\n- If `experimentService.isEnabled(\"hyde\")` and value is `\"enabled\"` → calls `hydeService.generateHypothetical(rewritten, userId)`\n- If HyDE available → `textToEmbed = hypotheticalAnswer`; otherwise falls back to `rewritten`\n- Used for both dense embedding and sparse encoding in the single-query path\n\n**(C) Experiment-aware answer generation:**\n- `aiProviderRegistry.generateSuggestion(ragContext)` → `aiProviderRegistry.generateSuggestion(ragContext, userId)`\n- Experiment assignments from the result are recorded in the audit context string via `enrichContextWithExperiments()`\n\n**New private helper:** `enrichContextWithExperiments(contextString, experiments)` — parses the JSON context string and adds `experimentAssignments` field.\n\n### `SemanticQueryServiceTest.java` changes\n- Added `@Mock` fields for `ExperimentService`, `HydeService`, `SqlQueryRouter`\n- Updated constructor call in `setUp()` to include the 3 new mocks\n- Added lenient stubs: `experimentService.isEnabled(anyString()) → false` and `sqlQueryRouter.canHandle(anyString(), any()) → false` so all existing tests pass unchanged\n- Updated `mockRagAnswer()` and `query_successfulPipeline_returnsCorrectSources` to use the 2-arg `generateSuggestion(context, any())`\n- **4 new tests:**\n  - `query_sqlRouterHandlesAnalyticalIntent_returnsSqlResultEarly` — SQL router handles the query, embedding never called, result has `HIGH` confidence tier\n  - `query_sqlRouterReturnsUnavailable_fallsThroughToVectorSearch` — SQL router fails, pipeline falls through to normal vector search\n  - `query_hydeExperimentEnabled_usesHypotheticalAnswerForEmbedding` — HyDE active, embedding called with hypothetical answer\n  - `query_hydeExperimentEnabled_butHydeFails_fallsBackToOriginalQuestion` — HyDE unavailable, fallback to original question\n  - `query_hydeExperimentDisabled_usesOriginalQuestionForEmbedding` — HyDE disabled, normal path, `hydeService` never called\n\nVerdict: changes_made"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":756,"cacheRead":204528,"cacheWrite":291,"totalTokens":205576,"cost":{"input":0.000003,"output":0.011340000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0613584,"cacheWrite":0.00109125,"total":0.07379265}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774824757487,"responseId":"msg_018ZeB2tEFd91Yn68MGY81eF"}}
