he provider is available before running the actual comparison across the test cases.\n\nSetting up the embedding comparison test...\n\nNow I'm iterating through a set of test queries and running them through both control and treatment embedding services, measuring the latency for each and collecting the results into a map that tracks the query, model names, and performance metrics. Logging the embedding test results with query preview and dimension counts, then moving into the report generation phase where I'm setting up the output directory and preparing to write the A/B comparison results to a JSON file with a timestamp.\n\nNow I'm populating the report structure with metadata about both the control and treatment models, then conditionally adding LLM and embedding comparison summaries based on whether there are results to include. I realize the Spring annotations are just metadata, so I can instantiate the service directly with the constructor parameters. For the A/B comparison logic, I need to run each test case against both the control and treatment models, measuring schema validity, latency, and token usage, then determine a winner based on which model produces valid output faster.\n\nSince the providers track cumulative tokens, I'll capture the token count before and after each call to get the delta for that specific case. I'll use two separate provider instances initialized in setUp to keep the tracking clean. For the EmbeddingService, I should use the public constructor that takes the API key, base URL, model, and object mapper rather than the package-private one.\n\nWriting the test implementation... I can use the public constructor directly since it creates a real HttpClient with reasonable defaults. Now I'll write out the full implementation, keeping it straightforward without unnecessary complexity.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the information I need. Let me implement the changes:\n\n**1. Create `AbComparisonRunner.java`:**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01UkZrxFQx9LB2Dc3wy9VE7u","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/henrydegrasse/Development/GauntletAi/HPP/ST6V2/backend/src/test/java/com/weeklycommit/ai/eval/AbComparisonRunner.java","content":"package com.weeklycommit.ai.eval;\n\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.core.type.TypeReference;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode;\nimport com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper;\nimport com.weeklycommit.ai.provider.AiContext;\nimport com.weeklycommit.ai.provider.AiSuggestionResult;\nimport com.weeklycommit.ai.provider.OpenRouterAiProvider;\nimport com.weeklycommit.ai.rag.EmbeddingService;\nimport java.io.File;\nimport java.io.InputStream;\nimport java.nio.file.Files;\nimport java.nio.file.Path;\nimport java.time.Instant;\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.LinkedHashMap;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.Map;\nimport java.util.stream.Stream;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.AfterAll;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.BeforeAll;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Tag;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test;\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.TestInstance;\nimport org.slf4j.Logger;\nimport org.slf4j.LoggerFactory;\n\n/**\n * Offline A/B comparison runner for evaluating LLM model and embedding model\n * variants side-by-side.\n *\n * <p>\n * Tagged with {@code @Tag(\"ab-eval\")} so it is excluded from both normal\n * {@code ./gradlew test} and the existing {@code evalTest} task. Run explicitly\n * with:\n *\n * <pre>\n * ./gradlew abEvalTest\n * </pre>\n *\n * <p>\n * Environment variables:\n * <ul>\n * <li>{@code OPENROUTER_API_KEY} — required; tests skip gracefully if\n * absent.</li>\n * <li>{@code AB_CONTROL_MODEL} — LLM control arm (default:\n * {@code anthropic/claude-sonnet-4}).</li>\n * <li>{@code AB_TREATMENT_MODEL} — LLM treatment arm (default:\n * {@code google/gemini-2.5-flash-preview}).</li>\n * <li>{@code AB_CONTROL_EMBEDDING} — embedding control model (default:\n * {@code openai/text-embedding-3-small}).</li>\n * <li>{@code AB_TREATMENT_EMBEDDING} — embedding treatment model (default:\n * {@code openai/text-embedding-3-large}). NOTE: this is for offline eval\n * only — the live Pinecone index is fixed at 1536-d and cannot accept\n * 3072-d vectors from text-embedding-3-large.</li>\n * </ul>\n *\n * <p>\n * Output: {@code build/eval-results/ab-comparison-{timestamp}.json} with\n * per-case scores and aggregate summary (mean score, win rate, latency,\n * token usage).\n */\n@Tag(\"ab-eval\")\n@TestInstance(TestInstance.Lifecycle.PER_CLASS)\nclass AbComparisonRunner {\n\n\tprivate static final Logger log = LoggerFactory.getLogger(AbComparisonRunner.class);\n\n\tprivate static final String DEFAULT_CONTROL_MODEL = \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4\";\n\tprivate static final String DEFAULT_TREATMENT_MODEL = \"google/gemini-2.5-flash-preview\";\n\tprivate static final String DEFAULT_CONTROL_EMBEDDING = \"openai/text-embedding-3-small\";\n\tprivate static final String DEFAULT_TREATMENT_EMBEDDING = \"openai/text-embedding-3-large\";\n\tprivate static final String OPENROUTER_BASE_URL = \"https://openrouter.ai/api/v1\";\n\tprivate static final int MAX_TOKENS = 1024;\n\n\tprivate final ObjectMapper objectMapper = new ObjectMapper();\n\n\tprivate boolean providerAvailable;\n\tprivate String controlModel;\n\tprivate String treatmentModel;\n\tprivate String controlEmbeddingModel;\n\tprivate String treatmentEmbeddingModel;\n\n\tprivate OpenRouterAiProvider controlProvider;\n\tprivate OpenRouterAiProvider treatmentProvider;\n\tprivate EmbeddingService controlEmbeddingService;\n\tprivate EmbeddingService treatmentEmbeddingService;\n\n\tprivate final List<Map<String, Object>> llmCaseResults = new ArrayList<>();\n\tprivate final List<Map<String, Object>> embeddingCaseResults = new ArrayList<>();\n\n\t// ── Setup ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n\t@BeforeAll\n\tvoid setUp() {\n\t\tString apiKey = System.getenv(\"OPENROUTER_API_KEY\");\n\t\tif (apiKey == null || apiKey.isBlank()) {\n\t\t\tlog.warn(\"OPENROUTER_API_KEY not set — A/B eval tests will be skipped\");\n\t\t\tproviderAvailable = false;\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tcontrolModel = System.getenv().getOrDefault(\"AB_CONTROL_MODEL\", DEFAULT_CONTROL_MODEL);\n\t\ttreatmentModel = System.getenv().getOrDefault(\"AB_TREATMENT_MODEL\", DEFAULT_TREATMENT_MODEL);\n\t\tcontrolEmbeddingModel =\n\t\t\t\tSystem.getenv().getOrDefault(\"AB_CONTROL_EMBEDDING\", DEFAULT_CONTROL_EMBEDDING);\n\t\ttreatmentEmbeddingModel =\n\t\t\t\tSystem.getenv().getOrDefault(\"AB_TREATMENT_EMBEDDING\", DEFAULT_TREATMENT_EMBEDDING);\n\n\t\tcontrolProvider = new OpenRouterAiProvider(apiKey, controlModel, MAX_TOKENS, OPENROUTER_BASE_URL,\n\t\t\t\tobjectMapper);\n\t\ttreatmentProvider = new OpenRouterAiProvider(apiKey, treatmentModel, MAX_TOKENS, OPENROUTER_BASE_URL,\n\t\t\t\tobjectMapper);\n\t\tcontrolEmbeddingService =\n\t\t\t\tnew EmbeddingService(apiKey, OPENROUTER_BASE_URL, controlEmbeddingModel, objectMapper);\n\t\ttreatmentEmbeddingService =\n\t\t\t\tnew EmbeddingService(apiKey, OPENROUTER_BASE_URL, treatmentEmbeddingModel, objectMapper);\n\n\t\tproviderAvailable = true;\n\t\tlog.info(\"A/B Comparison Runner initialised:\");\n\t\tlog.info(\"  LLM  control:    {}\", controlModel);\n\t\tlog.info(\"  LLM  treatment:  {}\", treatmentModel);\n\t\tlog.info(\"  Emb  control:    {}\", controlEmbeddingModel);\n\t\tlog.info(\"  Emb  treatment:  {}\", treatmentEmbeddingModel);\n\t}\n\n\t// ── LLM A/B comparison ────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n\t/**\n\t * Runs the LLM A/B comparison across commit-draft-assist and rag-query golden\n\t * datasets. For each case, both control and treatment models are invoked and\n\t * their schema validity, latency, and token usage are compared.\n\t */\n\t@Test\n\tvoid runLlmAbComparison() throws Exception {\n\t\tif (!providerAvailable) {\n\t\t\tlog.info(\"Skipping LLM A/B comparison — provider unavailable\");\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\trunLlmCasesForDataset(\"eval/commit-draft-assist/cases.json\", AiContext.TYPE_COMMIT_DRAFT,\n\t\t\t\tthis::buildCommitDraftContext,\n\t\t\t\toutput -> output != null && output.has(\"suggestedTitle\") && output.has(\"suggestedEstimatePoints\"));\n\n\t\trunLlmCasesForDataset(\"eval/rag-query/cases.json\", AiContext.TYPE_RAG_QUERY,\n\t\t\t\tthis::buildRagQueryContext,\n\t\t\t\toutput -> output != null && output.has(\"answer\") && output.has(\"confidence\"));\n\t}\n\n\t// ── Embedding A/B comparison ──────────────────────────────────────────\n\n\t/**\n\t * Runs the embedding A/B comparison using representative planning queries.\n\t *\n\t * <p>\n\t * This is the correct place for embedding model A/B evaluation: it creates\n\t * separate {@link EmbeddingService} instances per model and calls the real API,\n\t * but does <em>not</em> touch the live Pinecone index. The 1536-d control\n\t * (text-embedding-3-small) matches the index dimension; the 3072-d treatment\n\t * (text-embedding-3-large) is only evaluated offline here.\n\t */\n\t@Test\n\tvoid runEmbeddingAbComparison() throws Exception {\n\t\tif (!providerAvailable) {\n\t\t\tlog.info(\"Skipping embedding A/B comparison — provider unavailable\");\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t// Representative planning queries drawn from the rag-query golden dataset\n\t\t// plus additional analytical / compliance questions\n\t\tList<String> testQueries = deriveEmbeddingTestQueries();\n\n\t\tfor (String query : testQueries) {\n\t\t\tMap<String, Object> caseResult = new LinkedHashMap<>();\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"query\", query);\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"controlModel\", controlEmbeddingModel);\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"treatmentModel\", treatmentEmbeddingModel);\n\n\t\t\t// Control embedding\n\t\t\tlong controlStart = System.currentTimeMillis();\n\t\t\tfloat[] controlVector = controlEmbeddingService.embed(query);\n\t\t\tlong controlLatencyMs = System.currentTimeMillis() - controlStart;\n\n\t\t\t// Treatment embedding\n\t\t\tlong treatmentStart = System.currentTimeMillis();\n\t\t\tfloat[] treatmentVector = treatmentEmbeddingService.embed(query);\n\t\t\tlong treatmentLatencyMs = System.currentTimeMillis() - treatmentStart;\n\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"controlDimensions\", controlVector.length);\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"treatmentDimensions\", treatmentVector.length);\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"controlSuccess\", controlVector.length > 0);\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"treatmentSuccess\", treatmentVector.length > 0);\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"controlLatencyMs\", controlLatencyMs);\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"treatmentLatencyMs\", treatmentLatencyMs);\n\n\t\t\tif (controlVector.length > 0) {\n\t\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"controlVectorMagnitude\", computeL2Magnitude(controlVector));\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t\tif (treatmentVector.length > 0) {\n\t\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"treatmentVectorMagnitude\", computeL2Magnitude(treatmentVector));\n\t\t\t}\n\n\t\t\t// Cosine similarity is not directly comparable between 1536-d and 3072-d\n\t\t\t// vectors; flag this in the report\n\t\t\tcaseResult.put(\"dimensionMismatch\", controlVector.length != treatmentVector.length);\n\n\t\t\tembeddingCaseResults.add(caseResult);\n\t\t\tlog.info(\"Embedding A/B — query='{}...' control={}d({}ms) treatment={}d({}ms)\",\n\t\t\t\t\tquery.substring(0, Math.min(45, query.length())),\n\t\t\t\t\tcontrolVector.length, controlLatencyMs,\n\t\t\t\t\ttreatmentVector.length, treatmentLatencyMs);\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\t// ── Report ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n\t@AfterAll\n\tvoid writeReport() throws Exception {\n\t\tif (llmCaseResults.isEmpty() && embeddingCaseResults.isEmpty()) {\n\t\t\tlog.info(\"A/B comparison: no results to report (provider unavailable or no cases loaded)\");\n\t\t\treturn;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tPath reportDir = Path.of(\"build\", \"eval-results\");\n\t\tFiles.createDirectories(reportDir);\n\t\tString timestamp = Instant.now().toString().replace(\":\", \"-\");\n\t\tFile reportFile = reportDir.resolve(\"ab-comparison-\" + timestamp + \".json\").toFile();\n\n\t\tMap<String, Object> report = new LinkedHashMap<>();\n\t\treport.put(\"timestamp\", Instant.now().toString());\n\t\treport.put(\"controlModel\", controlModel);\n\t\treport.put(\"treatmentModel\", treatmentModel);\n\t\treport.put(\"controlEmbeddingModel\", controlEmbeddingModel);\n\t\treport.put(\"treatmentEmbeddingModel\", treatmentEmbeddingModel);\n\n\t\tif (!llmCaseResults.isEmpty()) {\n\t\t\treport.put(\"llmComparison\", buildLlmSummary());\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tif (!embeddingCaseResults.isEmpty()) {\n\t\t\treport.put(\"embeddingComparison\", buildEmbeddingSummary());\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tobjectMapper.writerWithDefaultPrettyPrinter().writeValue(reportFile, report);\n\t\tlog.info(\"A/B comparison report written to: {}\", reportFile.getAbsolutePath());\n\t\tlogSummary(report);\n\t}\n\n\t// ── Private: LLM case runner ──────────────────────────────────────────\n\n\tprivate void runLlmCasesForDataset(\n\t\t\tString resourcePath,\n\t\t\tString suggestionType,\n\t\t\tContextBuilder contextBuilder,\n\t\t\tSchemaValidator schemaValidator)\n\t\t\tthrows Exception {\n\n\t\tStream<EvalCase> cases = loadCases(resourcePath);\n\t\tcases.forEach(evalCase -> {\n\t\t\ttry {\n\t\t\t\trunSingleLlmCase(evalCase, suggestionType, contextBuilder, schemaValidator);\n\t\t\t} catch (Exception e) {\n\t\t\t\tlog.warn(\"LLM A/B case '{}' failed: {}\", evalCase.id(), e.getMessage());\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t});\n\t}\n\n\tprivate void runSingleLlmCase(\n\t\t\tEvalCase evalCase,\n\t\t\tString suggestionType,\n\t\t\tContextBuilder contextBuilder,\n\t\t\tSchemaValidator schemaValidator)\n\t\t\tthrows Exception {\n\n\t\tAiContext context = contextBuilder.build(evalCase);\n\n\t\t// ── Control ──\n\t\tlong controlTokensBefore = controlProvider.getTotalTokensUsed();\n\t\tlong controlStart = System.currentTimeMillis();\n\t\tAiSuggestionResult controlResult = controlProvider.generateSuggestion(context);\n\t\tlong controlLatencyMs = System.currentTimeMillis() - controlStart;\n\t\tlong controlTokensUsed = controlProvider.getTotalTokensUsed() - controlTokensBefore;\n\n\t\tboolean controlSchemaValid = false;\n\t\tJsonNode controlOutput = null;\n\t\tif (controlResult.available() && controlResult.payload() != null) {\n\t\t\ttry {\n\t\t\t\tcontrolOutput = objectMapper.readTree(controlResult.payload());\n\t\t\t\tcontrolSchemaValid = schemaValidator.isValid(controlOutput);\n\t\t\t} catch (Exception ignored) {\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t// ── Treatment ──\n\t\tlong treatmentTokensBefore = treatmentProvider.getTotalTokensUsed();\n\t\tlong treatmentStart = System.currentTimeMillis();\n\t\tAiSuggestionResult treatmentResult = treatmentProvider.generateSuggesti
